General.Name: ALM Equity AB (publ)
General.Description: ALM Equity AB (publ), through its subsidiaries, operates as a real estate development company in Sweden. It operates through Property Management, Project Development, Contracting, and Digital Services segments. The company provides property development services for housing, service, and commercial properties. It also offers turnkey contracting services for new builds, extensions or refurbishing of properties, as well as other contracting services for specific parts of property projects. In addition, the company develops smart digital services in a mobile platform primarily focused on the property sector that simplify communication, access, availability, and sharing economy in properties. ALM Equity AB (publ) was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
